name: Double Down (DNAStudio.dev)
description:
A fast paced arcade game, where you drive a car and deliver a package to a certain checkpoint. Or at least try to. Avoid cops and traffic that try to block your path and help yourself with an interactive minimap. Drive safe!

Sources for used audio:
